---
title: Sticky Asian Pork & Pickled Veggie Tacos with Cucumber & Sriracha Mayo
description: Here’s another taco night with a flavour-fusion twist! This time, we’re packing our warm tortillas with sticky stir-fried pork mince, zingy pickled veggies and crunchy cos lettuce. A sprinkle of chilli, mint, and crispy shallots add even more texture and flavour!
